long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your ClickFunnels experience with this extension that turns your ClickFunnels into a dark mode theme.

Just enable the extension and visit your ClickFunnels account and you will be greeted with an entirely new design that matches the ClickFunnels 2.0 experience.
